{"tid":2394513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【蜘蛛俠3】Tom Holland 肥仔friend準備黑化","createTime":"2021-02-04T08:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T08:38:48.000Z","uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9585df81abe05d110cb4906f61a104c204db2df2","tid":2394513,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/17/47/1511347585-ned-leeds-spider-man-homecoming.jpg?resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F17%2F47%2F1511347585-ned-leeds-spider-man-homecoming.jpg%3Fresize%3D480%3A%2A&h=ff1b6bc4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《蜘蛛俠3》演員陣容，無論是超級英雄還是反派，傳聞都非常誇張。除了傳出三代蜘蛛俠會同框演出外，外媒更確認了奇異博士將會加入；至於反派陣營，則有奧斯卡影帝Jamie Foxx確認自己重新飾演電魔，而外媒曾多番報道劇組有意找來前兩代《蜘蛛俠》系列電影的反派加入。之後早前在網上流出的《蜘蛛俠3》片場照，見到又有疑似新反派出現。沒想到，近日SONY繼續發力，暗示有重要成員或會變成反派。 <br />\n<br />\n而官方日前則貼出新IG Story，見到由Jacob Batalon飾演的Peter Parker好友Ned Leeds，身上竟多了一個重要標誌，莫非在暗示Ned Leeds將會黑化，成為粉絲期待而久的反派Hobgoblin？  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/96/77/81/967781d8f349fcbb26aed90821a34717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F96%2F77%2F81%2F967781d8f349fcbb26aed90821a34717.jpg&h=e760f966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/583130/%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A03-sony%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%87%E9%80%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%8D%E6%B4%BE%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A0%E6%AD%BB%E9%BB%A8%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E9%BB%91%E5%8C%96?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment&amp;fbclid=IwAR13ubBFdc1W7OuEwSd6wheFxlCzT9e1jaPQwICB7rQnm7EJmxbkM7cmUyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F583130%2F%25E8%259C%2598%25E8%259B%259B%25E4%25BF%25A03-sony%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258A%2587%25E9%2580%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%